  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13095389/inghams-in-safe-hands-charcoal.png?width=500&amp;height=126.45687645687646" alt="in safe hands" data-udi="umb://media/afba17a916e84fcc848acce5dda4f9c4" /></p>
<h2>Extra peace of mind for your next holiday</h2>
<p>We've been helping you explore your passions for over 85 years. You're in safe hands when you book with us and to give you extra peace of mind we've put extra measures in place to help keep you and your money safe.</p>
<p> </p>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<p><img style="width: 100px; height: 100px;" src="/media/13105952/with-you-every-step-100x100.jpg?width=100&amp;height=100" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/6cfb2870ca2d4d4cb8e9dbfc1a5dea09" /></p>
<p><strong>With you all the way </strong></p>
<p>We are here for you before, during and after your holiday.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<p><img style="width: 100px; height:100px;" src="/media/13105953/abta-protected-100x100.jpg?width=100&amp;height=100" alt="ABTAProtect" data-udi="umb://media/4b04bd1786d04f768b07000154dffa16" /></p>
<p><strong>ATOL &amp; ABTA protection</strong></p>
<p>These schemes are backed by the government, so whatever happens, your money is protected.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<p><img style="width: 100px; height: 100px;" src="/media/13105951/in-safe-hands-100x100.jpg?width=100&amp;height=100" alt="SafeHands" data-udi="umb://media/603db46afcb94dd0873b5d2870c04272" /></p>
<p><strong>We’re in a strong position</strong></p>
<p>We’re part of a much bigger family of businesses. Our parent company is a large Swiss supermarket and retailer called Migros, so as a group, we’re stronger together.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<p><img style="width: 100px; height:100px;" src="/media/13105954/low-deposit-100x100.jpg?width=100&amp;height=100" alt="LowDeposit" data-udi="umb://media/19f1279eb86a47bbb7b6af6403fdd360" /></p>
<p><strong>Low deposit</strong></p>
<p>Reserve your holiday for just £150 per person.</p>
<p>Your final balance will be due 10 weeks before departure. For some dates we might need to increase the deposit a little to secure your choice of flights.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<p><img style="width: 100px; height:100px;" src="/media/13105955/fee-free-100x100.jpg?width=100&amp;height=100" alt="FeeFree" data-udi="umb://media/b3da26ed04884ae084fa4dd1f2290775" /></p>
<p><strong>Fee-free flexibility on all holidays </strong></p>
<p>Flexibility to move your holiday to a later date, up to the point that your full balance is due, with no admin fee from us. You can move your holiday to any other holiday or date currently on sale. You will need to cover any extra cost if your new date is more expensive and this can only be done once. If our suppliers charge a fee for the change we may need to pass this on.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<p><img style="width: 100px; height:100px;" src="/media/13105956/snow-guarantee-100x100.jpg?width=100&amp;height=100" alt="SnowG" data-udi="umb://media/b1d76dae2856456286509c15ea448230" /></p>
<p><strong>Snow Guarantee </strong></p>
<p>No Snow? S’no problem. We only feature high altitude resorts with reliable snow records, but if your resort is fully closed, we’ll do our best to get you back on the slopes. (<a rel="noopener" data-udi="umb://document/f4ae07b2d50a4681918f9b4a3d6500c6" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f4ae07b2d50a4681918f9b4a3d6500c6}" target="_blank" title="Snow Guarantee" data-anchor="#">T&amp;Cs apply</a>). </p>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p><br /><br /></p>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h2 align="center" style="text-align: center;">Staying safe</h2>
<p style="text-align: left;" align="center"><span data-sheets-value="{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;We’ll do our very best to make sure your holiday is everything you expect it to be. Wherever we can, we’ll let you know about changes in advance, but sometimes it might be at very short notice.\r\nTaking care\r\n\r\nAll partner hotels will be managed by their own local, professional teams - compliant with local laws and regulations of that country. We only work with very carefully chosen, trusted partners.\r\nFor the accommodation we manage, we will always be compliant with local laws of that country and all of our staff will have appropriate training.  \r\n\r\nWhile travelling, in some countries and regions, you may need to wear face coverings when you’re in public areas, both indoors and outside. Do check the local regulations before you travel and bring a few spares.\r&quot;}" data-sheets-userformat="{&quot;2&quot;:961,&quot;3&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:0},&quot;9&quot;:0,&quot;10&quot;:1,&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0}"><strong>Taking care</strong></span> </p>
