</ul>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h2 align="center">With you every step</h2>
<strong>Preparing for your holiday</strong>
<ul>
<li>We’re available for any advice while you’re thinking about booking, or preparing to go away. Just call us and we’ll help.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>While you’re away</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>When you’re on holiday, our overseas staff will be there to support you if you need it and are just a phone call away. You’re never on your own.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Over 85 years of trust and experience </strong></p>
<p><img style="width: 193px; height: 193px; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/media/13094739/85_logo-193.jpg?width=193&amp;height=193" alt="85Years" data-udi="umb://media/c36b68d22a3c4ab086e644b960d38939" /></p>
<strong>You can judge us by our reviews</strong>
<ul>
<li><span>Our customers have spoken, and their words are our credibility. We proudly boast a 4.7 out of 5 rating on Feefo. Read what they have to say about us <a rel="noopener" href="https://www.feefo.com/en-GB/reviews/inghams?displayFeedbackType=BOTH&amp;timeFrame=YEAR" target="_blank" title="inghams feefo reviews" data-anchor="?displayFeedbackType=BOTH&amp;timeFrame=YEAR">here</a>.</span></li>
</ul>
<strong>Be prepared with Travel Insurance</strong>
<ul>
<li>Inghams is an Unregulated Introducer of Campbell Irvine Ltd who are authorised and regulated by the <a rel="noopener" href="https://www.fca.org.uk/" target="_blank" title="FCA">Financial Conduct Authority</a>.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>FCDO Travel advice</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Travellers are advised to read the FCDO travel advice for the country they are travelling to. Visit <a style="font-size: small;" rel="nofollow noopener" href="https://www.gov.uk/foreign-travel-advice" target="_blank">gov.uk/foreign-travel-advice</a></li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>]]></bodyText>
